A **proof-of-work** is the verifiable result obtained through a given work. Anyone should be able to make sure that a given share of work was accomplished.

This is used in bitcoin for blocks generation. The block hash itself is a proof-of-work, proving whoever generated that block deserves the associated transaction fees and reward.

